Friday, January 20, 1995

MOTION DOCKET

95-85. No. 94APA04-492. State v. Tyler. Franklin County,

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and a claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution of the court of appeals’ judgment,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, granted, effective January 19, 1995.
